snippet.title: LIVE : India's Republic Day Parade 26th January, 2025 | गणतंत्र दिवस  | 26 January Parade Live
snippet.description:
India celebrates the 76th Republic Day on 26th January 2025. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 76th Republic Day Parade on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the tenth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan. 

#RepublicDayOnDD #IndianRepublicDay2025 #RepublicDayFullParade #IndianArmy #IndiacelebratesRepublicDay #RepublicDaycelebrations #IndianNationalFlag #GantantraDivasParade #HappyRepublicDay #republicday2025  #76thRepublicDay #RepublicDayParade2025  #PMModi #AmarJawanJyoti #PatrioticVideo #BikestuntsbyIndianArmy #NarendraModi #DDNational #DoordarshanLIVE #Rajpath #IndiaGate #MinistryofDefence #RepublicDay #WarMemorial #गणतंत्रदिवस #RepublicDay #RepublicDayparade #republicday2025  #RepublicDay  #RepublicDayparade #republicday2025   #indiarepublicday

DD National blends a healthy mix of entertainment, information and education. All major National events like Republic Day Parade, Independence Day Celebrations, National Award Presentation ceremonies, President and Prime Minister’s addresses to the Nation,  President’s address to the joint session of Parliament, important Parliamentary debates, Budget presentations, involving India and other important sporting encounters are also telecast live.

snippet.title: Mass Jathara - Mass Rampage Glimpse | Ravi Teja, Sreeleela | Bheems| S Naga Vamsi | Bhanu Bogavarapu
snippet.description:
The Swag. The Energy. The Vibe. 🔥🔥🔥

𝐌𝐀𝐒𝐒 𝐌𝐀𝐇𝐀𝐑𝐀𝐀𝐉 Ravi Teja is here to deliver an ALL ROUND SHOW! 😎❤️‍🔥

#MassJathara ~ Mass Rampage Glimpse out now 💥 #HappyBirthdayRaviTeja ❤️

#MassJathara is an upcoming film Starring Ravi Teja & Sreeleela in Lead Roles. Written & Directed by Bhanu Bogavarapu. Music by Bheems Ceciroleo. Cinematography by Vidhu Ayyanna. Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naga Vamsi S & Sai Soujanya Under Sithara Entertainments & Fortune Four Cinemas. Presented by Srikara Studios.

snippet.title: KHADPANCH | Episode 1 - P.O.V | Latest Punjabi Web Series 2025 | ਖੜਪੰਚ All Episodes Available on YT
snippet.description:
In a small village plagued by a rising tide of drug-related deaths, the mysterious overdose of a young man named Babbu sparks a web of suspicion and intrigue.

After the success of "Yaar Jigree Kasooti Degree" and "Yaar Chale Bahar"  Troll Punjabi is back with a Mystery Series "KHADPANCH" - A gripping tale of a Punjab's Village torn apart by addiction, secrets, and the relentless pursuit of justice.


Edited, Produced, Written & Directed - Rabby Tiwana (Insta :-  @rabbytiwana)

Starring - Amrit Amby (IG : @amritamby),  Sukh Pindi Wala AKA Dhutta (IG : @pindi_ala),  Amrita Amme (IG : @Amrita Amme), Butta Badbar (IG : @buttabadbar).

Theme Song Credits
Vocals - Gurpreet Singh, Gron Sukhija
Music - Gurpreet Singh (Hertz Music Studio)
Lyrics - Kunwar Partap

Challi Jandi Ee Credits
Singer/Lyrics/Compose: Rythm Mansa
Music/Mix/Master: IGMOR
Link :  https://youtu.be/sLNbOkDLoSc

snippet.title: Computing with Soap | बंटी का साबुन Slow नहीं, Super Computer से भी तेज हें | Ep 1  - 3030 Eklavya
snippet.description:
For registration and more details, please visit: https://eklavya.iitgandhinagar.ac.in/

Homework/Assignment Link: https://tinyurl.com/eklavyahw1

About the Episode: A soap film can solve some of the most difficult problems of finding the optimum path between cities. Why do bees make hexagons not square or pentagons for their beehives? We will explore optimization properties of natural elements i.e. light, electricity, gravity and see how beautifully natural laws are interconnected.

Topics Covered
Surface Tension, Area and Perimeter, 2D Geometry, 3D Geometry, Mensurations, Snell’s Law, Reflection, Refraction, Total Internal Reflection, Optics, Cell Structure, Cell Division, Chemistry of Soap, Motion and Algebra, Shortest and Fastest Path, 




Timestamps of Computing with Soap 

Welcome, Introduction: 04:00   
Mission and Vision: 04:40
New perspective of Soap: 07:10
Poll 1 - हम स्कूल क्यों जाते हैं ? : 10:02
What’s in the new season: 10:41 
Today’s preview: 11:48
Poll 2 - Fermat’s Point: 14:53 
Surface Tension Property : 18:00
Hydrogen Bonding: 20:28 
Poll 3 - मेट्रो सबसे तेज कौन बना सकता है?  : 24:21 
Area and Perimeter: 26:53
Soap and Beehive: 29:30
Poll 4 - The fastest path between points A & B is? : 31:09 
Optically analogy from Soap: 33:50
Fastest Descent Problem: 40:40 
Catenary Curve: 43:20
Giant Bubble and Colors : 45:10
Making of Soap: 47:10
Soap and Cell: 47:48
End and Thank you speech: 48:50

Soap Making: https://drive.google.com/file/d/19bpBAgFjIiE8ZbcOb-D6bbyVf12QEIaB/view?usp=drive_link 



Fermat’s Point : 
DIY Models : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tPDDX3ARi_B5XqLr4C_ljdT1s5JwS9zZ/view?usp=drive_link 
GeoGebra: Optmized path in mediums with different speed - https://www.geogebra.org/classic/d8ggzmfp 
https://www.geogebra.org/classic/qsntsfqy
Fermat Principle: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermat%27s_principle

Optically analogy from soap : 
Hoffman, Dale T. "Smart soap bubbles can do calculus." The Mathematics Teacher 72.5 (1979): 377-389.
Optimum Path : https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qUXRQBHLwDVLn-J5Adia8fwu3JidAQQL/edit?usp=sharing&ouid=113177858658528269238&rtpof=true&sd=true
Worksheet: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cOnHlHB88STEjKpkmhhP9vbzB_cO5IVo/view?usp=sharing 

Fastest Descent Problem : 
Brachistochrone problem - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brachistochrone_curve

Soap Film for different curve: 
Reference - Criado, Carlos, and Nieves Alamo. "Solving the brachistochrone and other variational problems with soap films." American Journal of Physics 78.12 (2010): 1400-1405

3D Geometry and soap: 
Alum, Benedict Nnachi. "Saponification Process and Soap Chemistry." Inosr Applied Sciences 12.2 (2024): 51-56.

Soap and cell: 
Soap Making : https://drive.google.com/file/d/19bpBAgFjIiE8ZbcOb-D6bbyVf12QEIaB/view?usp=drive_link 
.

Books:
Steinhaus, Hugo. Mathematical snapshots. Courier Corporation, 2012
Lovett, David, and John Tilley. Demonstrating science with soap films. CRC Press, 2017
Chapter - The Steiner Graphs. Gardner, Martin. The last recreations: hydras, eggs, and other mathematical mystifications. American Mathematical Soc., 2020.


Previous episodes of 3030 Eklavya: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kcq7Z2T8Ndk&list=PLmjuVk9xK8LraYfCi9G-675V81ECptFyz

Previous episodes of 3030 Stem: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CHyRGlnJcO0&list=PLmjuVk9xK8LoorOK9Wk1zCS3EGu_M1BdS

Website: https://ccl.iitgn.ac.in
________
About Us

We came into being to nurture a scientific temperament among adults and children alike. Our journey began from an empty 400 sqft room, and today, 7 years later, we have a hall full of 1000+ unique STEM models and activities, created / curated / expanded by us. Having conducted over 200 STEM and hands-on learning workshops for over 20,000 teachers & professors and connected with over 500,000 students nationwide - our mission is to bring back the gleam in their eyes!

Write to us at ccl@iitgn.ac.in
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ccl_iitgn/

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Valladolid 0-3 Real Madrid | LaLiga 2024/25
snippet.description:
LaLiga leaders Real Madrid recorded their fourth consecutive league victory in Valladolid and increased their lead over second-placed Atlético to four points. Ancelotti's men gave a very solid performance, going into half-time with a 1-0 lead after Mbappé showed his goal-scoring prowess again on the half-hour mark. The Frenchman, who has found the net in his last five games, was again decisive after the break: he extended the lead in the 57th minute before completing his first hat-trick as a Real Madrid player in added time by converting a penalty. Our team is top yet again.

es.title: RESUMEN | Valladolid 0-3 Real Madrid | LaLiga 2024/25
es.description:
El Real Madrid, líder de la Liga, sumó en Valladolid su cuarta victoria consecutiva en la competición y aumentó a cuatro puntos su distancia sobre el Atlético, segundo clasificado. Los de Ancelotti completaron un partido muy serio, en el que se fueron al descanso con 0-1 tras una nueva demostración de pegada de Mbappé a la media hora de juego. Tras el descanso, el francés, que ha visto puerta en los cinco últimos partidos, volvió a ser determinante: amplió distancias en el 57’ y firmó su primer hat-trick como madridista en el añadido al transformar un penalti. Nuestro equipo es más líder.

snippet.title: Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon | Sky Force | Akshay, Sara, Veer, Tanishk B, Arijit Singh, Afsana Khan, Irshad
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of love with Tu Hai Toh Main Hoon from Sky Force! This soulful melody, sung by Arijit Singh and Afsana Khan, beautifully captures the essence of love and togetherness. Featuring Veer Pahariya and Sara Ali Khan, with lyrics by Irshad Kamil and music by Tanishk Bagchi, this song will surely strike a chord in your heart.

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Song Credits:
Song name - Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon
Singer - Arijit Singh , Afsana khan
Music - Tanishk Bagchi 
Lyrics - Irshad kamil
Starcast - Veer Pahariya, Sara Ali Khan
Programming - Tanishk Bagchi
Additional Programming- Krishna Kishore
Drums - Stuart Brown ( Scotland )

Lyrics:-

Subhe subhe subhe subhe teri yaadein
Subhe subhe subhe subhe din bana de
Tu meri kheedkiyo pe bikhre din banke
Tu mujhpe dhoop sa hai girta chan chan ke
Chan chan ke

Tu ishq hai toh main baahon mein hoon
Baahon mein hoon toh panaahon mein hoon
Kajal hoon toh main nigahon mein hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Kasme vaade kyun tu hain toh main hoon
Bas main tera hoon tu hain toh main hoon
Seene pe likh loon tu hain toh main hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Antara:
Ek mutthi khwahishon ki tere aage khol ke
Zindagi bhar chup rahoonga baatein dil ki bol ke
Na tere saaye pe bhi aaye koi aanch dua maangoon
Main sadke main tere apni khushi de doonga tol ke

Tu rang mein, teri pehchaan hoon
Pehchaan hoon, main teri jaan hoon
Main koi tera hi armaan hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Jhoothe Judaiyan
Jhoothe  bichhode
Yaad kisi ka haath na chhode
Yaad kahe yeh humse aksar
Tu hain toh main hoon

snippet.title: 10 BEST DISHES I Tried In Mumbai!! Part 1 ☕️🍨 🤤
snippet.description:
Mumbai is a food lover’s paradise, and I explored it to the fullest! From iconic street eats to luxurious gourmet dishes, I tried over 65 amazing dishes on this trip, but these 10 truly stood out.

Kicking things off is the frothy cold filter coffee at Benne – the perfect balance of strength and sweetness for just ₹40! Then there’s the nostalgic Banana Walnut Ice Cream at K. Rustom’s, packed with flavor and crunch. At Opedro, the tangy Fish Ceviche was an explosion of freshness, while the Coffee Rasagulla Sundae at Bombay Canteen redefined desserts with its bold innovation. Finally, the ultra-premium New Zealand Lamb Chops at La Panthère were a melt-in-your-mouth indulgence worth every bite.

Want to know the top five dishes? Head to Part 2!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Galaxy S25 Ultra First Look - The KING Of AI Smartphones🔥🔥🔥
snippet.description:
Namaskaar Dosto, yeh ek bahut hi kamaal video hai jaha pe maine aapse baat ki hai Samsung Galaxy S25 Series ke baare mein aur isi ke ek first look ke baare mein. snippet.title: રાકેશ બારોટ | ચોરસો પારકા ની પીઠી | Chorso Paraka Ni Pithi | Rakesh Barot | New Bewafa Song 2025
snippet.description:
રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું ગુજરાતી બેવફા ગીત "ચોરસો પારકા ની પીઠી" સાંભળો, માત્ર  @SaregamaGujarati    પર.

Check out the new Gujarati bewafa song by Rakesh Barot, "Chorso Paraka Ni Pithi" only on   @SaregamaGujarati   💔🎶


Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot 
Producer: Red velvet cinema 
Lyrics: Janak Jesangpura, Jigar Jesangpura 
Music: Mehul Barot 
Artist: Rakesh Barot , Neha Suthar, Bobby Kalpesh 
Co.artist: Lata prajapati, Ramesh thakor,Darbar
Dop: Montu Rajput 
Editing: Kishor Rajput 
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manish R barot
Spot boys: Kiran Thakor , Kabhai
Makeup: Hashmukh Limbachiya
Hair Dresser: Rinku Nai
Ass.Director: Babusinh Thakor
Poster Design: Aman Agola
Production: Satubha Thakor 
Crowd: Nayan Thakor 
Light's: Kalpesh Jadav

Lyrics: 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે (2 )
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે..તમે ચોરસો પારકાની પીઠી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે ને ,થશે લગ્ન ની તારા વિધિ 
એ ટાઈમ મેં મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
હે હાથ મા શ્રીફળ ગોથેનો ચારે કોર 
ઓગને વેચાય તારા સગપણ નો ગોળ 
હે પારકે બોઘીયા સબન્ધ (૨)
પેહરી તે સગાઈ વીંટી ,મારા કાળજા મારા દલ ને નાખિયું વેધી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
હો તારી સગાઈ નો ફોટો સ્ટેટ્સ મા ચઢશે 
જોઈ ને ફોટો મારુ કાળજું રે બળશે 
હો આજે તારી સગાઇ કાલે લગ્ન તું કરશે 
પારકું પાનેતર પહેરી ચોરી એ તું ચઢશે 
આવું બધું વિચારે મન હીબકે ડોલે દલ 
જુદા થવાની આજ કેવી લાગે મને પળ 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે..તમે ચોરસો પારકાની પીઠી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
પારકા પિયુ સાથે લગન તું કરશે 
મારા સાચા પ્રેમ ના ધજાગરા રે ઉડશે 
ઓ તારા લગન ને મારુ મોત આવે દુકડુ 
ઓઢેલા પાનેતર તું મને ધોળું લૂગડું

Lyrics: 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે (2 )
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે..તમે ચોરસો પારકાની પીઠી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે ને ,થશે લગ્ન ની તારા વિધિ 
એ ટાઈમ મેં મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
હે હાથ મા શ્રીફળ ગોથેનો ચારે કોર 
ઓગને વેચાય તારા સગપણ નો ગોળ 
હે પારકે બોઘીયા સબન્ધ (૨)
પેહરી તે સગાઈ વીંટી ,મારા કાળજા મારા દલ ને નાખિયું વેધી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
હો તારી સગાઈ નો ફોટો સ્ટેટ્સ મા ચઢશે 
જોઈ ને ફોટો મારુ કાળજું રે બળશે 
હો આજે તારી સગાઇ કાલે લગ્ન તું કરશે 
પારકું પાનેતર પહેરી ચોરી એ તું ચઢશે 
આવું બધું વિચારે મન હીબકે ડોલે દલ 
જુદા થવાની આજ કેવી લાગે મને પળ 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે..તમે ચોરસો પારકાની પીઠી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી 
પારકા પિયુ સાથે લગન તું કરશે 
મારા સાચા પ્રેમ ના ધજાગરા રે ઉડશે 
ઓ તારા લગન ને મારુ મોત આવે દુકડુ 
ઓઢેલા પાનેતર તું મને ધોળું લૂગડું 
હો તારે હરખ ની વેળા મારે રોમ ના તેડાં 
તમે જાસો સાસરે અમે જાસું ઉપર વેહલા 
હે લગ્ન કરશો બીજે રે..તમે ચોરસો પારકાની પીઠી 
એ સમય મારા મોત ની ફાટશે ચીઠી (2 )

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

So Google has developed a new Quantum Computer called Willow, which can perform a highly complex calculation in just 5 minutes, a task that would take the world's fastest supercomputers 700 trillion times the age of the universe to complete . But how is this even possible?
In the previous video of this series, we explored how computers evolved from a 2,000-year-old mechanical device to billions of transistors packed into microprocessors. We examined how technology advanced, the scientific laws we harnessed, and how this incredible journey has brought us to the dawn of a new era – The Quantum Age. In today’s video we take the series further by discussing how exactly does a Quantum computer work, what is the basics of Quantum computing and finally the unrealistic uses of this technology. So let's dive in...Hope you stay Quantum Entangled till the end of the video ;)

09:31 Sponsor

snippet.title: Snow Day Vlog in Tamil | Making a Snow Man | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me during our recent experience with snow fall. We had never experienced this heavy snow before and we had a great time playing with snow balls and we also built a snowman. Alandra had a great time playing in the snow. We had already protected the cold sensitive plants in the greenhouse and wrapped others. It was a very good experience having snow as a temporary guest and seeing the whole landscape in a bright white color. 

Friends, hope you like today's vlog. See you soon with more interesting vlogs.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | PSG 4-2 MAN CITY | Grealish, Haaland Goals | UEFA Champions League
snippet.description:
City will need to beat Club Brugge next week to qualify for the Champions League play-off round after a 4-2 defeat to PSG.
The Blues saw a two -goal lead slip against the impressive French champions who responded with an outstanding fight-back

After a goalless first-half, quickfire second period goals from Jack Grealish and Erling Haaland looked to have set City on the road to a priceless victory.

But two goals in four minutes for PSG wiped out our advantage in the blink of an eye, a third from Joao Neves 12 minutes from time and a Gonçalo Ramos fourth with the last kick of the game gave the Ligue 1 champions a dramatic 4-2 win.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.
